# Force LF line endings across all platforms.
# Rationale: Phase 2 upstream-snapshot.test.ts pins SHA-256 of data/templates/*.json;
# Windows autocrlf would convert LF→CRLF on checkout and break the hash invariant.
# Global `eol=lf` ensures consistent bytes in working tree everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary — never touch
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf binary
*.db binary
*.db-wal binary
*.db-shm binary
*.enc binary
